 privatesector financial institutions  and may announce their plans this month     the alliance is in part aimed at helping bridge the divide between the postal group and privatesector banks which have long accused it of crowding them out ahead of this falls initial public offering of shares in japan post holdings and its banking and insurance units     japan post bank likely would put up half of their new companys several hundred million yen in initial capital with sumitomo mitsui trust and the nomura group contributing roughly  and  respectively the three have informed financial regulators of their plans which call for launching the company next year     japanese post offices already sell various mutual funds and other investment products the joint venture would seek to cater to an underserved segment of customers preferring safe depositlike vehicles for their money it also would offer personal definedcontribution retirement savings plans and wrap accounts which let investors delegate the management of their portfolios sales of these products would begin at select locations and eventually expand nationwide     japan post bank sees the venture as a launchpad for an asset management business with access to a network of  post offices it hopes to ride a shift in personal finance from savings to investment being promoted by the government and seized on by privatesector financial institutions the bank is trying to show investors that its strategy for postipo growth points in this direction     nomura holdings the parent of nomura securities hopes the venture will broaden its own retail customer base by creating new investors it can contribute knowhow on explaining financial products to beginners for the past few years its sales efforts have emphasized building assets over the medium to long term rather than earning sales commissions and its assets under management have grown     sumitomo mitsui trust sees joining forces with the postal group as a way to level the playing field with japans three megabanks which boast far bigger branch networks it brings strength in product development that draws on years of experience managing corporate pensions nomura holdings inc japan marketticker tks sectorindustry financeinvestment banksbrokers market capusd m shares m about nomura holdings inc sumitomo mitsui trust holdings inc japan marketticker tks sectorindustry financeregional banks market capusd m shares m about sumitomo mitsui trust holdings inc print facebook twitter linkedin google mail related companies nomura holdings inc sumitomo mitsui trust holdings inc capital nomura securities public co ltd related stories breaking even japan post financial units pick up slack for ailing postal arm reform from the top top execs bring nomura in sight of tn yen asset goal changes at japan post banking arm aims to be investment firm get insights on asia in your inbox register about newsletters more in deals cheung kong property clinches deal for german smartmeter company malaysias scientex hunting for north american acquisitions delta china eastern each acquiring  of air france shares follow nikkei asian review the best content posted the latest headlines tweeted follow nar nikkei asia index  airasia to take wing in japan after long layover japan samsung ends intels year run as topselling chipmaker south korea north america kweichow moutai gulps higher firsthalf profit on broader liquor lineup chinahong kong cheung kong property clinches deal for german smartmeter company chinahong kong europe more news and indexes about asia receive our newsletters register follow nikkei asian review frequent posts of the best content the latest headlines tweeted follow nar latest headlines toshiba to give western digital notice on closing memory sale rd creativity crucial to ride out sea change toyota honorary chairman trump replaces chief of staff priebus after sixmonth run with kelly airasia to take wing in japan after long layover north korea nd icbm test put